author: Marina Villeneuve and Lori Hinnant / AP
title: New York City Coronavirus Deaths Now Outnumber 9/11 Ground Zero Toll
description: New York City’s death toll from the coronavirus officially eclipsed the number of those killed at the World Trade Center on 9/11, health officials said Tuesday.
content:
(NEW YORK) — New York City’s death toll from the coronavirus officially eclipsed the number of those killed at the World Trade Center on 9/11, health officials said Tuesday. In Britain, Prime Minister Boris Johnson was in intensive care with the virus.
